From: zhengbin <zhengbin13@huawei.com>
Date: Wed, 22 Jan 2020 15:53:11 +0800
Subject: drm/amd/powerplay: use true, false for bool variable in smu7_hwmgr.c
Git-commit: a16afcdd8c58285e83951ce318b55eafb7948997
